<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>JESUH A RA LIO CH170</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Hlaphuah u si, Pathian Fa a tum lai, Thi in khamhnak a hmumi vialte
 ca, A rung tum lai i a kan cawi dih lai, Jesuh a rung tum than lai.

[C1]
   Jesuh a rungtum lai, rung tum than lai, Jesuh a rung tum than lai;
   (a rung tum than lai) Khua kip ah Pathian lawmhnak hla thek u, Jesu a
   rung tum than lai.

[V2]
 Jesuh tum tikah mithi an tho lai, Kan sianlomi he kan i tong dih lai,
 Vancung Pathian sinah kan kai dih lai, Jesuh a rung tum than lai.

[C2]
   Jesuh a rungtum lai, rung tum than lai, Jesuh a rung tum than lai;
   (a rung tum than lai) Khua kip ah Pathian lawmhnak hla thek u, Jesu a
   rung tum than lai.

[V3]
 Jesuh a tum lai, mithiang a khamh lai, Ral thawhnak vawlei kha a
 daihter lai, Ngaihchiat thinphan sualnak a lo dih lai, Jesuh a rung tum
 than lai.

[C3]
   Jesuh a rungtum lai, rung tum than lai, Jesuh a rung tum than lai;
   (a rung tum than lai) Khua kip ah Pathian lawmhnak hla thek u, Jesu a
   rung tum than lai.

[V4]
 Ka ra lai tiah biakam a pel lai lo, Pathian thim ciami ahodah an si?
 Jesuh a ngangmi ahodah an si? Jesuh a rung tum than lai.

[C4]
   Jesuh a rungtum lai, rung tum than lai, Jesuh a rung tum than lai;
   (a rung tum than lai) Khua kip ah Pathian lawmhnak hla thek u, Jesu a
   rung tum than lai.</lyrics>
<key>Bb</key>
<hymn_number>170</hymn_number>
</song>